Calibre is meant to be a complete e-library solution.
It includes library management, format conversion, news feeds to ebook
conversion as well as e-book reader sync features. Calibre is
primarily a ebook cataloging program. It manages your ebook collection
for you. It is designed around the concept of the logical book, i.e.
a single entry in the database that may correspond to ebooks in
several formats. It also supports conversion to and from a dozen
different ebook formats.
